{
  "info": {
    "name": "Inventory Management API - Muhammad Daffa Raihan",
    "_postman_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
    "description": "Postman collection untuk Inventory Management API milik Muhammad Daffa Raihan.\n\nCollection ini mencakup:\n- Auth (Register & Login)\n- Items CRUD (Create, Read, Update details, Delete)\n- Update Stock dengan aturan bisnis (IN/OUT, tidak boleh negatif)\n- Activity Logs untuk setiap perubahan stok\n\nDirancang untuk demo/tes backend dengan struktur folder rapi dan response yang konsisten.\n\n**CARA PENGGUNAAN:**\n1. Import collection ini ke Postman\n2. Pastikan variable {{base_url}} sudah diset (default: http://localhost:3000)\n3. Jalankan request Register terlebih dahulu\n4. Jalankan request Login - token akan otomatis tersimpan\n5. Semua request lainnya akan otomatis menggunakan Bearer token dari login",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Kumpulan request untuk autentikasi user (register & login) menggunakan JWT.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Daffa\",\n  \"email\": \"daffa@gmail.com\",\n  \"password\": \"daffa123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "register"
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"daffa@gmail.com\",\n  \"password\": \"daffa123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "let json = null;",
                  "try {",
                  "  json = pm.response.json();",
                  "} catch (e) {",
                  "  console.log('Tidak bisa parse JSON response login:', e);",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "if (json) {",
                  "  // Coba ambil token dari beberapa kemungkinan struktur response",
                  "  let token = null;",
                  "  if (json.data && json.data.token) {",
                  "    token = json.data.token;",
                  "  } else if (json.token) {",
                  "    token = json.token;",
                  "  } else if (json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
                  "    token = json.data.accessToken;",
                  "  } else if (json.accessToken) {",
                  "    token = json.accessToken;",
                  "  }",
                  "",
                  "  if (token) {",
                  "    // Simpan ke collection variable supaya semua request otomatis pakai",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', token);",
                  "    console.log('✅ Token berhasil diset! Semua request sekarang akan otomatis menggunakan Bearer token ini.');",
                  "  } else {",
                  "    console.log('❌ Token tidak ditemukan di response login. Periksa struktur response API Anda.');",
                  "  }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
